♪ WASH YOUR MAKE ♪

11:13.839 --> 11:15.716
♪ BLUE LAKE RIVER TOILET CAKES ♪

11:15.800 --> 11:17.843
[SIGHING]

11:17.927 --> 11:19.095
BEN, SHUT THE WINDOW.

11:19.178 --> 11:20.971
{\an1}I CAN'T LISTEN
TO THAT SONG ANYMORE.

11:21.055 --> 11:23.099
Crowd: ♪ BLUE LAKE RIVER
TOILET CAKES ♪

11:23.182 --> 11:26.143
WELL, IT'S BETTER
THAN EVERYONE SAYING KAJOLICA.

11:26.227 --> 11:27.103
[EXPLOSION]

11:27.186 --> 11:31.190
[BEEPING...]

11:32.525 --> 11:38.489
[♪...]

11:50.793 --> 11:53.963
{\an5}Bessie: EACH YEAR,
THERE IS ONE DAY
IN THE LIFE OF A HONEYBEE

11:54.046 --> 11:57.216
THAT IS MORE SPECIAL
THAN ALL THE REST.

11:57.299 --> 12:01.095
{\an5}IT IS THE MORNING, EACH SPRING,
AS FLOWERS BLOSSOM,
AND BEES BUZZ

12:03.431 --> 12:07.810
THAT THE YEAR'S FIRST BATCH
OF HONEYBEE TAFFY IS BORN.

12:07.893 --> 12:12.148
FRESH OFF THE CONVEYOR BELT,
DELICIOUS NEW PIECES

12:12.231 --> 12:16.986
{\an5}ARE LOVINGLY WRAPPED,
BOXED UP, AND DELIVERED
RIGHT TO OUR DOORSTEPS

12:19.321 --> 12:24.452
AND WITH THAT THUD, THE HEART
OF EVERY HONEYBEE SKIPS A BEAT.

12:24.535 --> 12:28.289
IT IS THE START OF
THE TAFFY-SELLING SEASON.

12:29.206 --> 12:33.961
{\an3}REJOICE.

12:34.044 --> 12:35.337
[CRASHING]

12:35.421 --> 12:37.006
Both: IT'S HERE, IT'S HERE,
IT'S HERE, IT'S HERE!

12:37.089 --> 12:42.803
[SQUEALING...]

12:52.688 --> 12:55.399
TO ANOTHER SPECTACULAR
TAFFY-SELLING SEASON.

12:57.234 --> 12:59.445
[GULPING]

12:59.528 --> 13:01.822
[GROANING]

13:05.242 --> 13:09.705
PENNY, DOES THIS TAFFY
TASTE RIGHT TO YOU?

13:09.788 --> 13:11.332
[GULPING]

13:11.415 --> 13:15.878
IS IT ME, OR IS IT... DIFFERENT?

13:16.962 --> 13:18.506
MM, DELICIOUS.

13:18.589 --> 13:20.299
DELICIOUS.

13:20.382 --> 13:21.550
OF COURSE IT IS.

13:21.634 --> 13:24.178
IT'S HONEYBEE TAFFY.

13:24.261 --> 13:27.223
{\an5}I HAD KUNG PAO CHICKEN
FOR LUNCH, SO MY TASTE BUDS
ARE PROBABLY JUST SHOT.

13:27.306 --> 13:28.182
[GULPING]

13:28.265 --> 13:31.477
[GAGGING]

13:31.560 --> 13:32.394
[GROANING]: YUMMY.

13:38.567 --> 13:40.236
{\an3}HEY, HAPS.

13:40.319 --> 13:43.906
{\an6}I KNOW I'M NOT
SUPPOSED TO DISTURB YOU
WHEN YOU'RE FENG "SHUI-ING"

13:43.989 --> 13:45.074
BUT I NEED A SECOND OPINION.

13:45.157 --> 13:49.078
{\an1}WILL YOU TASTE THIS TAFFY
AND TELL ME WHAT YOU THINK?

13:49.578 --> 13:51.455
IT'S FINE, RIGHT?

13:51.539 --> 13:52.498
SAME AS EVER?

13:56.168 --> 13:57.920
{\an1}HAPPY!

13:58.003 --> 14:05.261
I'M INVOICING YOU.

14:05.261 --> 14:08.806
[SIGHING]

14:08.889 --> 14:09.473
[SCREAMING]

14:09.557 --> 14:10.099
HEY, MRS. GIBBONS.

14:10.182 --> 14:11.850
CAN YOU TASTE THIS TAFFY?

14:11.934 --> 14:15.437
I THINK IT MIGHT BE... OFF.

14:15.521 --> 14:17.106
TASTE TAFFY?

14:17.189 --> 14:18.607
YOU KNOW I'M SLIMMING.

14:18.691 --> 14:20.985
GIVE IT.

14:21.068 --> 14:22.903
[CHEWING]

14:22.987 --> 14:26.365
STANDARD ISSUE.

14:26.448 --> 14:30.703
ARE YOU SURE?

14:30.786 --> 14:33.122
'CAUSE WE'RE SUPPOSED TO START
SELLING TAFFY IN TWO DAYS.

14:33.205 --> 14:36.625
I'VE BEEN EATING TWO BOXES
A DAY FOR 20 YEARS.

14:36.709 --> 14:37.167
I THINK I SHOULD KNOW.

14:37.251 --> 14:38.419
TWO BOXES?

14:38.502 --> 14:40.879
ONE AND A HALF.

14:40.963 --> 14:43.132
LEAVE US.

14:43.215 --> 14:45.009
Bessie: OH, FINGER.

14:45.092 --> 14:48.345
{\an5}MRS. GIBBONS AND 100
HONEYBEE TAFFY INSPECTORS
CAN'T BE WRONG, RIGHT?

14:49.096 --> 14:50.848
I GUESS IT'S JUST ME.

14:50.931 --> 14:52.182
I'M PROBABLY COMING DOWN
WITH SOMETHING.

14:52.266 --> 14:55.185
[GULPING]

14:55.269 --> 14:58.480
[GLASS BREAKING]

14:58.564 --> 15:01.859
[GROANING]

15:01.942 --> 15:03.319
[GAGGING]

15:08.365 --> 15:10.826
1946, SAME.

15:10.909 --> 15:13.787
1987, SAME.

15:13.871 --> 15:16.832
2003, SAME.

15:16.915 --> 15:20.294
NEW TAFFY, SAME.

15:20.377 --> 15:23.631
CONSISTENCY.

15:23.714 --> 15:25.841
[SCREAMING]

15:25.924 --> 15:28.427
CONSISTENT.

15:28.510 --> 15:30.679
WHAT IS IT WITH THIS TAFFY?

15:30.763 --> 15:32.097
THINK, BESSIE, THINK.

15:32.181 --> 15:35.643
{\an5}IT LOOKS THE SAME,
IT FEELS THE SAME,
IT SMELLS THE SAME

15:35.726 --> 15:37.978
BUT IT DOESN'T TASTE THE SAME!

15:40.773 --> 15:42.316
MIRIAM, POTENTIAL PROBLEM.

15:42.399 --> 15:44.818
TAFFY-SELLING STARTS
IN 24 HOURS.

15:44.902 --> 15:46.612
SHIPMENT POSSIBLY TAMPERED WITH.

15:46.695 --> 15:47.529
EN ROUTE TO FACTORY.

15:47.613 --> 15:48.280
SEEKING TRUTH.

15:48.364 --> 15:51.325
{\an3}[GRUNTING]

15:51.408 --> 15:52.868
[CAR HORNS HONKING]

15:57.498 --> 15:59.249
[MECHANICAL WHIRRING]

15:59.333 --> 16:01.126
HELLO?

16:01.210 --> 16:01.794
HELLO?

16:01.877 --> 16:03.754
Man: YES, MAY I HELP YOU?

16:03.837 --> 16:04.588
OH, HI.

16:04.672 --> 16:05.214
BESSIE HIGGENBOTTOM, TROOP 828?

16:05.297 --> 16:08.133
NO?

16:08.217 --> 16:10.719
YOU MAY THINK I'M CRACKERS
FOR ASKING THIS

16:10.803 --> 16:15.974
{\an5}BUT HAVE YOU, IN ANY WAY,
ALTERED THE TAFFY-MAKING
PROCESS THIS YEAR?

16:16.058 --> 16:18.394
{\an1}CERTAINLY NOT,
BUT WE APPRECIATE YOUR CONCERN.

16:18.477 --> 16:18.894
IT'S BEES LIKE YOU...

16:18.977 --> 16:20.521
NOTHING AT ALL?

16:20.604 --> 16:21.563
A NEW MIXING BOWL?

16:21.647 --> 16:23.357
DIFFERENT LIGHT BULBS?

16:23.440 --> 16:25.984
{\an6}I DON'T KNOW,
DID YOU CHANGE THE AMOUNT
OF LOVE IN EACH PIECE?

16:26.068 --> 16:27.611
POSITIVELY NOT.

16:27.695 --> 16:29.029
IT COULD BE SOMETHING TINY.

16:29.113 --> 16:31.198
{\an3}ARE ALL EMPLOYEES REQUIRED
TO WASH THEIR HANDS?

16:31.281 --> 16:32.741
{\an3}'CAUSE SOME PEOPLE SAY THEY DO,
AND THEY DON'T.

16:32.825 --> 16:34.827
{\an3}I MEAN, WATER, SOAP,
THE WHOLE DEAL?

16:34.910 --> 16:36.954
{\an3}DO YOU HAVE SIGNS UP
AND EVERYTHING?

16:37.037 --> 16:39.498
I CAN SEE A TRUE
TAFFY LOVER LIKE YOU

16:39.581 --> 16:40.833
ISN'T GOING TO BE SATISFIED
UNTIL YOU SEE FOR YOURSELF.

16:40.916 --> 16:43.502
HOW WOULD YOU LIKE
AN OFFICIAL TOUR?

16:43.585 --> 16:45.462
SO LET'S GET STARTED!

16:49.258 --> 16:52.302
{\an6}SINCE 1937, HONEYBEE TAFFY
HAS BEEN MADE
WITH ALL-NATURAL HONEY

16:52.386 --> 16:54.096
{\an3}PRODUCED BY OUR VERY OWN
SWARM OF HONEYBEES.

16:54.179 --> 16:56.557
OK, OK, THIS IS GOOD.

16:56.640 --> 16:58.267
VERY IMPRESSIVE.

16:58.350 --> 17:00.686
HONEYBEE TAFFY IS MIXED
RIGHT HERE IN THIS ROOM.

17:00.769 --> 17:01.729
Bessie: AWES...

17:05.482 --> 17:07.651
{\an6}AND AS YOU CAN SEE,
THE TAFFY DROPS OUT
OF THE MACHINE, ON TO THE BELT

17:07.734 --> 17:09.528
AND INTO THE BOX.

17:12.990 --> 17:15.784
MIND IF I EXAMINE
YOUR TASTE BUDS?

17:15.867 --> 17:17.327
Tour guide: AND THAT'S OUR TOUR.

17:17.411 --> 17:18.787
ANY QUESTIONS?

17:18.871 --> 17:20.079
WHAT'S BEHIND THAT DOOR?

17:20.164 --> 17:20.705
WHAT DOOR?

17:20.789 --> 17:21.123
Bessie: THAT DOOR.

17:21.205 --> 17:21.957
WHICH ONE?

17:22.040 --> 17:22.624
{\an3}THAT ONE.

17:22.708 --> 17:23.459
Tour guide: WHICH ONE?

17:23.541 --> 17:25.002
{\an3}THE DOOR YOU'RE STANDING
IN FRONT OF.

17:25.085 --> 17:25.836
{\an1}WHICH ONE?

17:25.919 --> 17:27.337
THE ONE YOU DON'T WANT TO OPEN.

17:27.421 --> 17:29.965
{\an1}STORAGE.

17:30.048 --> 17:30.632
CAN I JUST...?

17:30.716 --> 17:31.800
THANK YOU FOR VISITING.

17:31.884 --> 17:32.676
HAVE A GREAT DAY.

17:32.760 --> 17:33.844
{\an1}BYE.

17:37.973 --> 17:42.978
[WHIMPERING...]

17:44.772 --> 17:48.358
[BEES BUZZING...]

17:48.442 --> 17:51.779
[CHEWING]

17:51.862 --> 17:53.572
[DISTORTED VOICE]:
ANY QUESTIONS?

17:53.655 --> 17:56.158
ANY QUESTIONS?

17:56.241 --> 17:58.202
ANY QUESTIONS?

17:58.285 --> 17:59.703
ANY QUESTIONS?

17:59.787 --> 18:01.830
[SCREAMING]

18:01.914 --> 18:02.206
WE CAN'T SELL BAD TAFFY.

18:15.844 --> 18:17.930
{\an1}[GROANING]

18:18.013 --> 18:18.555
{\an1}[GRUNTING]

18:18.639 --> 18:22.142
{\an1}[GROANING]

18:24.102 --> 18:29.316
{\an1}SHH...

18:34.947 --> 18:40.452
[METAL DETECTORS SQUEAKING...]

19:07.563 --> 19:09.690
[BEEPING]

19:15.863 --> 19:17.155
[GASPING]

19:17.239 --> 19:23.537
WHAT IS THIS SECRET WORLD
OF INCONSISTENCIES?

19:23.620 --> 19:28.041
{\an5}[ALL TALKING AT ONCE]

19:23.620 --> 19:28.041
Portia: MOMMY, SHE RUINED
TAFFY SEASON.

19:28.125 --> 19:29.334
{\an3}[BUZZING]

19:29.418 --> 19:30.752
SETTLE DOWN, BEES.

19:30.836 --> 19:33.797
I JUST CAN'T BELIEVE
BESSIE TOOK MY TAFFY.

19:33.881 --> 19:35.924
I THOUGHT IT WAS SANTA.

19:36.008 --> 19:37.009
[SIGHING]

19:37.092 --> 19:39.595
I ALWAYS KNEW
SHE HAD A DARK SIDE.

19:39.678 --> 19:42.347
ANYWAY,<i> PROBLEMO</i> SOLVED.

19:42.431 --> 19:46.476
{\an5}YOU'RE ALL GETTING
EMERGENCY INVENTORY, COURTESY OF
THE HONEYBEE TAFFY FACTORY.

19:46.560 --> 19:48.061
EVERYONE, ON TO THE BEE BUS.

19:48.145 --> 19:49.730
<i>ANDALE, ANDALE.</i>

19:56.069 --> 20:01.909
Bessie: 91% PURE FAKE HONEY,
FROM CONCENTRATE?

20:03.327 --> 20:04.411
[GASPING]

20:12.377 --> 20:14.171
SECURITY BREACH!

20:14.254 --> 20:14.671
SOUND THE ALARM!

20:14.755 --> 20:17.049
[ALARM BLARING]

20:17.132 --> 20:17.841
Mrs. Gibbons: GO, GO, GO.

20:17.925 --> 20:20.802
HONEYBEE TAFFY FACTORY.

20:20.886 --> 20:21.887
{\an3}OH, WOW.

20:21.970 --> 20:23.513
THIS IS COOL.

20:23.597 --> 20:23.972
[SCREAMING]

20:24.056 --> 20:25.807
Man: GET HER!

20:25.891 --> 20:26.725
OH, NUTS.

20:35.734 --> 20:38.904
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

20:40.238 --> 20:43.158
[GRUNTING]

20:43.241 --> 20:47.537
I DEMAND AN EXPLANATION!

20:47.621 --> 20:53.126
WHY ARE YOU USING
91% PURE, FAKE HONEY?

20:53.210 --> 20:54.252
[GASPING]

20:54.336 --> 20:56.004
FROM CONCENTRATE?

20:56.088 --> 20:57.839
[GASPING]

20:57.923 --> 21:02.469
{\an5}HONEYBEE TAFFY HAS BEEN MADE
WITH PURE, GRADE-A HONEY
SINCE THE BEGINNING.

21:03.804 --> 21:08.892
{\an5}YOU EXPECT US TO LOOK
OUR CUSTOMERS IN THE EYE
AND LIE TO THEM?

21:09.768 --> 21:12.729
[CHUCKLING], NO.

21:12.813 --> 21:15.107
NOT TROOP 828, SIR.

21:15.190 --> 21:15.649
NOT ON MY WATCH.

21:15.732 --> 21:18.902
[CHEERING]

21:18.986 --> 21:20.779
LISTEN, MISSY.

21:20.862 --> 21:22.572
{\an1}YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND
THE BOTTOM LINE.

21:22.656 --> 21:24.324
{\an1}PURE HONEY'S TOO
EXPENSIVE THESE DAYS.

21:24.408 --> 21:29.955
{\an4}FAKE HONEY IS A COST-EFFECTIVE
SOLUTION DESIGNED TO MEET
THE DEMANDS OF THE MODERN WORLD.

21:30.372 --> 21:32.541
Woman: MODERN?

21:32.624 --> 21:36.253
A QUALITY PRODUCT
NEVER GOES OUT OF STYLE.

21:36.336 --> 21:38.380
MIRIAM BREEDLOVE!

21:38.463 --> 21:39.923
YOU GOT MY MESSAGES!

21:40.007 --> 21:44.219
{\an3}AND YOUR FAX, AND YOUR TEXT,
AND I EVEN SAW YOUR SIGNAL FIRE.

21:46.847 --> 21:51.435
{\an6}YOU, MY FRIEND,
OUGHT TO BE ASHAMED OF YOURSELF,
DISGRACING THE HONEYBEE NAME.

21:53.061 --> 21:54.646
GET RID OF THIS RIGHT NOW.

21:54.730 --> 21:56.231
ALL OF IT.

21:56.314 --> 21:59.985
{\an1}AND FOR YOU,
I HAVE A LITTLE SURPRISE.

22:02.863 --> 22:05.574
{\an1}APPROVED!

22:06.575 --> 22:11.538
[♪...]

22:48.492 --> 22:50.702
[CHILDREN LAUGHING]
